==Family and children==
With his wife Sidonie, Albrecht had nine children:
# [[Catherine of Saxony|Katharina]] (b. Meissen, 24 July 1468 - d. Göttingen, 10 February 1524), married firstly on 24 February 1484 in Innsbruck to Duke [[Sigismund of Austria]], and secondly on 1497 to Duke [[Erich I of Braunschweig-Kalenberg]].
# [[George, Duke of Saxony|Georg &quot;der Bärtige&quot;]] (b. Meissen, 27 August 1471 - d. Dresden, 17 April 1539).
# [[Henry IV, Duke of Saxony|Heinrich V &quot;der Fromme&quot;]] (b. Dresden, 16 March 1473 - d. Dresden, 18 August 1541).
# [[Duke Frederick of Saxony|Frederick]] (b. Torgau, 26 October 1474 - d. Rochlitz, 14 December 1510), Grand Master of the [[Teutonic Knights]].
# Anna (b. Dresden, 3 August 1478 - d. Dresden, 1479).
# Stillborn child (1479).
# Ludwig (b. Torgau, 28 September 1481 - d. Torgau?, some days later / d. Torgau?, young after 1498) [?].
# Johann (b. and d. Torgau, 24 June 1484).
# Johann (b. Torgau, 2 December 1498 - d. Torgau?, some days later / d. Torgau?, young in September of the same year as his brother Ludwig) [?].&lt;ref&gt;[http://www8.informatik.uni-erlangen.de/cgi-bin/stoyan/l1/LANG=span/INDEX=I276588 I276588: Josepha Octavia Mlinaric&lt;!-- Bot generated title --&gt;]&lt;/ref&gt;

